name: Isabelle - Animal Crossing
description:
Isabelle character from Animal Crossing

V2 Notes:

Learned a lot since V1, this version is waaay better at everything.

There's no trigger word for her outfit anymore, but that wasn't working on v1, outfits may be added on a newer version. Her green classic outfit can be rendered with the tags below.

Trigger words: isaCrossing

Recommended:

  • To render her iconic outfit: green cardigan, white shirt, blue skirt, red ribbon, checkered pattern

  • If you have trouble with her hair: topknot

  • To try and add fur: furry, furry female

  • Works fine at 1.0

//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

V1 Notes:

Trigger words: isaCrossing, isaClothes
(use isaClothes for the outfit)

Recommended:

  • To improve rendering her iconic dress: white shirt, green dress, blue skirt, red ribbon

  • To improve her hair: topknot

  • To improve fur: furry, furry female

  • Seems to work better at 0.9 or 0.8

Kinda glad with the results but it could get a lot better. Her outfit almost never comes out as it should just by using the isaClothes tag. Her hair also has problems, sometimes other animal's ears show up if topknot is not used or animal ears, cat ears are not in the negative prompt.

Training data will be attached and any feedback is welcome :)
